title: Tyson 2.0 Lightweight Disposable Vape 6K
inner_product_description: Compact yet powerful, the Tyson 2.0 Lightweight Disposable Vape 6K offers the ultimate vaping experience with 6000 total puffs across three devices. Each vape features 4ml of 5% nicotine salt e-liquid, ensuring strong, smooth hits. Advanced Fyre Mesh Coil technology enhances flavor consistency, while the rechargeable 550mAh battery provides reliable performance. With vibrant flavor options like Strawberry Watermelon and Cool Mint, this disposable vape is a must-have for flavor enthusiasts who value portability and convenience.

title: FLONQ Max Pro Vape
inner_product_description: The FLONQ Max Pro Vape combines cutting-edge features with sleek aesthetics. With 18ml of e-liquid and 20mg or 50mg nicotine options, it delivers over 20,000 puffs. Its dual mesh coil ensures rich, consistent flavor, while the boost mode elevates performance. A rechargeable 650mAh battery and an LED screen displaying battery, power, and e-liquid levels make it user-friendly. Perfect for those seeking a stylish and reliable vape.

title: Foger Switch Pro Disposable Pods
inner_product_description: Foger Switch Pro Disposable Pods push the limits of disposable tech with massive capacity and intuitive features. Boasting up to 30,000 puffs in normal mode or 18,000 in boost mode, this device doesn’t just last—it dominates. The smart screen display gives real-time usage stats, while dual mesh coils ensure rich, clean flavor with every hit. Adjustable airflow allows users to fine-tune their draw, and the 1050mAh rechargeable battery with Type-C support keeps it ready to go. Each unit holds 19mL of e-liquid with 5% nicotine for satisfying delivery and full-bodied flavor.

title: Trinity Spinny Vape 30K
inner_product_description: Elevate your vape game with the Trinity Spinny Vape 30K. Boasting a 25ml e-liquid capacity and dual mesh coils, it delivers exceptional flavor and vapor. Enjoy up to 4500 puffs with a rechargeable 800mAh battery and Type-C charging. Switch between two flavors effortlessly with its dual flavor feature, designed for both novices and pros seeking performance and style.
inner_feature_description: ['E-liquid Capacity: 25ml.', 'Coils: 2x Dual Mesh Coils.', 'Battery: 800mAh.', 'Charging: Type-C.', 'Dual Flavor Feature: Switch between two flavors effortlessly.', 'Operation: Press switch for easy use.', 'Designed For: Both beginners and experienced vapers.', 'Key Benefits: Combines performance, convenience, and versatility.', 'Watermelon Bubble Gum - Blue Razz Ice: Enjoy the juicy sweetness of watermelon bubble gum paired with the refreshing burst of blue raspberry ice for a cool and delightful vape.', 'Sex on the Beach - Spearmint: Experience the tropical blend of Sex on the Beach cocktail mixed with a crisp, invigorating spearmint finish.', 'Strawberry Yogurt Ice - Black Ice: Indulge in the creamy, sweet taste of strawberry yogurt complemented by the bold, cool sensation of black ice.', 'Pink Lemonade - Menthol: Savor the tangy, sweet flavors of pink lemonade with a refreshing menthol twist for a perfect balance of sweet and cool.', 'Mango Peach Watermelon - Gummy Bears: Delight in a fruity medley of mango, peach, and watermelon combined with the playful sweetness of gummy bears.', 'Kiwi Passionfruit Guava - Juicy Peaches: Relish the exotic trio of kiwi, passionfruit, and guava, enhanced by the luscious taste of juicy peaches.', 'Strawberry Ice Cream - Rainbow Candy: Enjoy the creamy richness of strawberry ice cream paired with the vibrant, sugary flavors of rainbow candy.', 'Strawberry Ice - Mango Ice: Experience the refreshing blend of icy strawberries and cool mango for a revitalizing and fruity vape.', 'Blue Raspberry Lemon - Strawberry Banana: Savor the tart, sweet mix of blue raspberry and lemon, perfectly balanced with the smooth, fruity taste of strawberry banana.', 'Strawberry Watermelon - Banana Ice: Delight in the classic combination of sweet strawberries and juicy watermelon, finished with a cool, icy banana touch.']

title: KV Turbo 25K Disposable Vape
inner_product_description: The KV Turbo 25K Disposable Vape offers up to 25,000 puffs with 18ml of pre-filled e-liquid, ensuring rich flavor and long-lasting use. Equipped with a large digital display for battery and e-liquid monitoring, it includes a rechargeable 750mAh battery with Type-C charging. Choose between two modes for extended vaping or enhanced flavor, all in a sleek design with dual coils for optimal performance.
inner_feature_description: ['18ml Pre-filled E-liquid: Provides up to 25,000 puffs with rich, flavorful clouds, minimizing the need for frequent refills.', 'Large Digital Display: Shows battery status, e-liquid level, and vaping modes for easy monitoring and control.', '750mAh Rechargeable Battery: Ensures long-lasting power with convenient Type-C recharging.', 'Two Vaping Modes: Offers a choice between 25,000 puffs in Mode 1 or 15,000 puffs in Mode 2 for enhanced flavor.', 'Dual Coils: Delivers optimal performance, making it ideal for mouth-to-lung (MTL) vaping.', '5% (50mg) Nicotine title: Foger Switch Pro Vape Kit
inner_product_description: Experience the Foger Switch Pro Vape Kit, a powerhouse disposable vape with 19mL of e-liquid, a 1050mAh battery, and a dual-mode option offering over 30,000 normal puffs or 18,000 boost puffs. Equipped with dual mesh coils, a smart screen display, and adjustable airflow for a tailored experience, this kit includes five devices per box (totaling 95mL). Rechargeable via Type-C, it also features overcharge protection for safe, long-lasting enjoyment.
inner_feature_description: ['Innovative Modular Design: The Foger Switch Pro stands out with its two-part design: a 200mAh disposable pod paired with an 850mAh magnetized charging dock that functions as a pass-thru charger, making it a more eco-friendly and cost-effective option.', 'Dual Vape Modes: Experience customizable vaping with Normal Mode, delivering up to 30,000 puffs, and Boost Mode, providing an intensified experience with up to 18,000 puffs.', 'High E-Liquid Capacity: Contains 19mL of e-liquid per device, offering a long-lasting vaping experience without the need for frequent replacements.', 'Powerful Battery: Equipped with a 1050mAh rechargeable battery, ensuring extended use and reliable performance.', 'Type-C Fast Charging: The super-fast Type-C charging port minimizes downtime and supports convenient, efficient recharging.', 'Transparent Tank: Features a clear tank design, allowing users to easily monitor e-liquid levels without any guesswork.', 'Smart Display Screen: The built-in display provides real-time information on battery level and puff count, keeping users informed and in control.', 'Adjustable Airflow: Customizable airflow settings enable users to fine-tune their vaping experience for optimal draw and flavor.', 'Dual Mesh 1.0Ω Coil: Advanced dual mesh coil technology ensures consistent flavor delivery and long-lasting coil life with a smooth, satisfying vapor.', 'Overcharge Protection: Safety features include overcharge protection, enhancing battery longevity and user safety.', 'Compact and Portable: At 96mm x 54.58mm x 27.66mm, the Foger Switch Pro is designed for convenience and portability.', 'Packing Details: Each box contains 5 devices (95mL total e-liquid per box), with 150 devices per carton, ideal for retailers.', 'Nicotine Strength: Available in a robust 50mg/ml for those who prefer a strong nicotine hit.', 'Blue Razz Ice – A frosty, tangy blue raspberry.', 'Blueberry Watermelon – A sweet blend of juicy blueberries and watermelon.', 'Coffee – Rich, bold coffee flavor for caffeine lovers.', 'Cool Mint – Refreshing, icy mint sensation.', 'Gum Mint – A classic gum flavor with a minty twist.', 'Gummy Bear – Sweet, nostalgic gummy candy flavor.', 'Juicy Peach Ice – Ripe, juicy peaches with a cool finish.', 'Kiwi Dragon Berry – Exotic kiwi, dragon fruit, and berry fusion.', 'Pineapple Coconut – Tropical blend of pineapple and creamy coconut.', 'Sour Apple Ice – Tart green apple with an icy hint.', 'Strawberry Banana – Smooth mix of strawberries and banana.', 'Strawberry Ice – Sweet strawberries with a chilling finish.', 'Strawberry Kiwi – Classic, refreshing strawberry and kiwi combo.', 'Strawberry Watermelon – Lush strawberries with a watermelon twist.', 'Watermelon Ice – Cool, refreshing watermelon flavor.', 'Miami Mint – A refreshing blast of crisp mint with a cool, invigorating exhale.', 'Sour Fcuking Fab – A mouth-puckering explosion of sour candy goodness with a sweet, fruity finish.', 'Sour Gush – A tangy and juicy mix of sour fruit flavors with a candy-like burst.', 'Sour Cranapple – Tart cranberries and crisp apples collide for a perfectly sour and sweet balance.', 'Sour Blue Dust – A zesty blue raspberry flavor with a sour kick and a sugary finish.', 'Strawberry B-POP – Fresh, ripe strawberries with a candy pop twist for a sweet and satisfying vape.', 'OMG B-POP – A vibrant medley of fruity candy flavors with an electrifying sweetness.', 'Mexico Mango – A bold and juicy mango flavor with a tropical twist, capturing the essence of ripe Mexican mangos.', title: Adjust MyFlavor Vape 40K
inner_product_description: Introducing Adjust MyFlavor Vape 40K, the 20mL pre-filled e-liquid disposable device, engineered for vape enthusiasts seeking both performance and flavor. Powered by a 5% (50mg) nicotine strength and a robust 800mAh Type-C rechargeable battery, this device delivers consistent and powerful vaping. With two distinct modes—Normal (40,000 puffs) and Burst (20,000 puffs)—it adapts to your preferences. The 6-level adjustable flavor settings ensure a personalized experience, all displayed on an interactive screen. The bite-friendly mouthpiece adds comfort for extended use, and the fully customizable design lets you fine-tune your vaping sessions.
inner_feature_description: ['High Puff Count: Up to 40,000 puffs in Normal Mode or 20,000 in Burst Mode.', 'Flavor Customization: 6 adjustable flavor levels for a tailored experience.', 'E-Liquid & Battery Indicators: Convenient display of e-liquid and battery levels.', 'Nicotine Strength: 5% (50mg) for a satisfying hit.', 'Battery Capacity: 800mAh, rechargeable via USB Type-C.', 'Dual Modes: Choose between Normal and Burst for versatile vaping.', 'Comfort Design: Bite-friendly mouthpiece for ease during extended use.', 'Advanced Heating: Dual mesh coils ensure smooth, flavorful vapor.', 'User-Friendly: Draw-activated operation with fixed airflow.', 'Blue Razz Ice: Dive into the vibrant world of Blueberry and Raspberry with a refreshing menthol twist. Adjust the ratio to suit your taste, whether you prefer a tangy blueberry base with subtle raspberry notes or a balanced blend of both berries, all cooled by a touch of ice.', 'Mixed Mint: Enjoy a unique fusion of Pepper Mint and Miami Mint for an ultra-refreshing vape. Customize your mint experience with the right mix of these fresh, crisp flavors, creating anything from a classic mint profile to a nuanced, cooling blend with distinctive minty undertones.', 'Orange Strawberry: Brighten your vaping session with zesty Orange and sweet Strawberry. Adjust for a citrus-forward vape with a hint of berry or opt for an even balance of these two flavors, creating a refreshing and fruity profile tailored to your preference.', 'Pineapple Ice Peach: Savor tropical Pineapple with smooth Ice Peach undertones. Choose your perfect blend ratio, emphasizing the juicy pineapple for a bolder taste or dialing up the cool peach notes for a balanced, refreshing vape with a cool twist.', 'Strawberry Banana: Classic meets creamy with Strawberry and Banana. Perfect your flavor experience by selecting a heavier strawberry note or amplifying the smoothness of banana, resulting in anything from a fruit-forward blend to a creamy strawberry-banana mix.', 'Tangerine White Gummy: Enjoy a nostalgic twist of Tangerine and White Gummy candy. Control the levels to enjoy either a citrusy, bright burst with a hint of candy sweetness or a gummy-inspired vape with a tangy tangerine edge.', 'Watermelon B-Pop: Go bold with Watermelon and a pop of B-Pop essence. Tweak your taste experience for a juicy watermelon-forward vape or dial up the bubblegum to add a touch of nostalgic sweetness to your session.', 'Watermelon Mango Peach: Explore the tropics with Watermelon, Mango, and Peach. title: Elf Bar BC5000 Vape
inner_product_description: Introducing Elf bar bc5000, a premium disposable option for vape shop owners. Each device is pre-filled with 9.5ml of e-liquid containing 50MG (5.0%) Nicotine. With approximately 5000 puffs per device and a 650mAh integrated battery, it promises long-lasting satisfaction. The disposable and rechargeable design ensures convenience. Featuring a dual mesh coil, it offers optimal flavor and vapor production. Stock your shelves with ebdesign bc5000 for an exceptional vaping experience. Buy Elf Bar BC5000 Clear Flavor here and Buy Elf Bar BC5000 Mint Tobacco Flavor here.

title: Digiflavor SKY 25K Disposable Vape

Featuring 5% nicotine strength, dual-mesh coils, adjustable airflow, and a 1.8" smart screen display, this vape ensures a top-tier experience. With USB-C charging and three firing modes, it's perfect for vape shops seeking high-quality wholesale products. Explore Digiflavor SKY Flavors for a diverse selection.

Built with high-quality materials, they guarantee a reliable and satisfying vaping experience. The compact and lightweight form factor makes it ideal for on-the-go vaping. title: Prime Bar 8000 Vape
inner_product_description: Discover the pinnacle of disposable vaping with the Prime Bar 8000, where rechargeability meets exceptional e-liquid capacity. Unlike traditional disposables, the Prime Bar 8000 is equipped with a rechargeable 650mAh battery, eliminating the need for oversized batteries and allowing for a compact design that fits in your palm.
